---
title: Mexican Cheesy Rice-Stuffed Poblanos with Avocado Salsa & Zesty Crema
description: Poblano peppers are perfect for stuffing. They’re mild, earthy, and sweet, plus, they stay a vibrant forest green once roasted. Chock full of savory ingredients like hearty whole grains, fresh tomato, and Southwestern spices, these packed peppers are sure to satisfy. They’re topped with melty Monterey Jack and avocado salsa, then finished off with a dollop of zesty crema and a sprinkle of chili.
